INSERT INTO [dbo].[articals] ([id], [title], [contenttype], [author], [publishtime], [content], [content-img], [content-img-trans]) VALUES (N'201704181611280', N'2nd annual VMA basketball tournament ends in thrilling conclusion', N'1', N'yumingmei', N'2017-03-31 23:55:00.0000000', N'["VMA is passionate about basketball; and our passion is fueled by a desire to promote friendship, teamwork, and competitive spirit. This year’s 2nd annual VMA basketball tournament was a triumph on all fronts, as 12 rounds of intense contests in 9 days culminated in a thrilling conclusion.","Each of VMA’s eight Houses fielded a team, and from the very first bounce of the ball, the basketball tournament commanded the community’s full attention. After many close preliminary contests, play-offs, and semifinals, Tang and Qing Houses were left to compete for the Championship.","The finals matched Tang House’s powerful offense against Qing House’s excellent defense: the irresistible force meeting the immovable object! Tang jumped in front early, but a quick adjustment in Qing’s strategy resulted in a see-saw battle and 9-6 Tang House lead at the end of the first quarter. Early in the second, Tang began to dictate the tempo of the game with increasingly speedy attacks, led largely by the skill and intensity of Li Jiheng. The breathtaking pace of the game captivated and energized the audience, as cheers grew louder and louder. Qing’s efforts to hold off Tang’s relentless attack proved unsuccessful, as did their attempts to counterattack. Lacking the fire-power to match Tang, Tang pulled away to 24-11 halftime lead.","During halftime, a street dance--“I got a boy”--entertained and amazed the spectators, while both teams used the time to discuss and adjust their strategy for the second half.","The third quarter featured a competition between the female teams from each House. Early anxiety quickly gave way to courage, as Li Xiang from Qing scored the first basket. However, Tang House won those points back with the help of a strong defense and excellent play from Zhai Zijing.","The male teams returned in the fourth quarter, and from the beginning it was clear that the break had benefited Qing. Proving that state of mind matters even more than skills, and with admirable determination and strong play from Lu Yang, Lu Zhenhua, and Peng Xiaofeng, Qing willed themselves into a 29-29 tie with only a few minutes left.","With the game on the line, and both Houses understandably nervous about the final minutes, Li Jiheng, eventual male scoring champion and tournament MVP, broke the tie and lifted Tang House to a hard-fought championship title, 33-29. ","In the following Monday Morning Assembly, awards (below) were announced and the entire academy enthusiastically congratulated all competitors on their excellent performance.","Individual Contribution Award","Lu Zhenhua, Zhang Jianli, Li Xiang, Xia Peiyu, Chen Jiaxin, Chen Chaowei, Luo Zheng, Tong Junbo, Du Xiaoshe, Wang Chunyuan, Wei Yuanhui, Jin Honghao, Peng Xiaofeng, Mo Junzhao, Yao Ziran, Gai Pengsheng, Jiao Hanjian, Li Jiheng, Lin Kai, Luo Ruihan","Team contribution Award ","Photography club: Sun Wanting, Huang Zi, Lin Kai, Xi Runqing, He Jiaqi","VMA Magazine club: Huang Yilin, Dong Yuran, Zhang Yuning, Wu Wanying, Deng Zhedan, Zeng Zishan","Street Dance club: Jing Tianwei, Yan Yining, Tang Ziying, Fu Yuqi, Huang Huixi, Zhu Xiaowei, Liu Zijin","Younth Volunteer club: Jiu Kaidi, He Jiaqi, Yang Yizhen, Peng Yubo, Huang Jiaxin, Zhou Huiru, Yan Yining, Li Sitao, Wang Tongyu, Yang Ailing, Wang Zhihang, Liu Sirui, Zheng Yawen, Huang Huixi, Fan Yecheng, Tan Zhenhua,Li Zhangfan, Yang Siqi, Luo Wanmeng, Zhang Yuning, Liu Sijin, Lin Ling, Liang Weijun, Zhang Qing, Ge Jing","Student Union: Tang Ziying, Jiang Yitao, Sun Wanting, Cao Hongwei, Liu Zijin, Fu Yuqi, Zhuang Yukun, Wang Yufan, Jing Tianwei, Tu Jiarui.","Scoring Champion","Li Jiheng, Li Xiang","Li Jiheng, Tian Xuwen","The Third Place","Song House: Li Xiang, Wang Chunyuan, Mo Zhenming, Chen Zixin, Jin Honghao, Yan Zhiqi, Yu Guanxiao, Wang Yulin, Liu Xingchen, Jing Tianwei, She Yilin, Wu Zhuoyang, Xu Yang, Liang Jiaxi, Zhu Xiaowei","The Second Place","Qing House: Lu Zhenhua, Peng Xiaofeng, Ma Pingyi, Lu Yang, Wang Zetian, Tang Qihang, Huang Peiyang, Tan Zhenhua, Gai Pengshen, Tang Ziying, Zheng Xing, Li Xiang, Ge Jing, Liu Sirui, Liu Zijin, Zhao Ruoyu.","Tang House: Luo Zhen, Cao Hongwei, Li Jiheng, Wang Yufan, Wu Zeshi, Dong Yuran, Luo Yuntian, Wang Zenan, Long Tianshu, Li Huchen, Luo Hongcheng, Yang Ling, Tian Xuwen, Fu Yuqi, Deng Zhedan, Huang Yaqi, Han Jiayue, Zhai Zijing","The Championship Ring is so cool!"]', N'["http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170418/6362812948727705863403321.png","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170418/6362812952353102409392090.png","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170418/6362812975483607789211887.png","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170418/6362812977640529106276504.png","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170418/6362813001652527534484000.png"]', N'["M甾服心D凹万科梅沙书","","万科梅沙书院","",""]')
GO
GO
