INSERT INTO [dbo].[articals] ([id], [title], [contenttype], [author], [publishtime], [content], [content-img], [content-img-trans]) VALUES (N'20160601140633', N'The famous architect Mr. Zeng Ren Zheng visited VMA', N'1', N'Admin', N'2016-06-01 14:20:53.0000000', N'["\n\tOn May 24, the\nfamous architect Mr. Zeng Ren Zheng, also called “Yu Shan”, was invited to\nVanke Meisha Academy (VMA). He presented us with his recent masterpiece on\nChinese landscape garden and brought students and teachers a feast of his\nsplendid ideas on arts and culture. He encouraged students to ponder over the\narts and culture in Chinese gardens, which is in concert with the VMA school\nmission of cultivating global citizens and leaders with Chinese identity. \n","\n\n\tMr. Zeng had been\nstudying Chinese garden architecture for many years and used to be an\narchitect. Later, he created his own paintings based on his thoughts: he\nbelieves there must be some connection between landscape and human\nself-cognition. Recently, he just published his new book, “The Garden of\nFantasies”. Prof. Dong Yugan from Peking University wrote the preface for this\nbook: “It will lead you a tour to the deep and the dark, the intermittently\nvisible and invisible, the soothing and the dense, the simple and the\ncomplicated, the distinct and the obscure. There might be leisure, solemnity,\nloneliness, or joy in his drawing of landscape and architecture.”\n","\n\n\tDuring this lecture,\nMr. Zeng illustrated some of his paintings and his thoughts behind that. His\npaintings perfectly convey his love and willingness to be close to nature. “If\nyou draw human beings in a painting of landscape, you are supposed to give them\nspecific meaning.” He is very good at seeking inspiration from architecture in\nChinese gardens. For instance, he showed us a tree growing next to a bridge,\nwhich arose from his thought “There must be Reiki between the tree and the\nbridge”. Then he drew a picture, expressing the similar meaning. Harmonious\nintegration of human being, nature, and architecture is what he has been\nstudying and painting. During the Q  A session, some of the students\ninterested in architecture had wonderful idea exchanges with Mr. Zeng. All the\nstudents and teachers attended and enjoyed his lecture. \n","\n \n\n\tMany students and parents have been confused about\nthe way we should place Chinese identity when we are educated to view the world\nfrom a global perspective. Ms. Wang He, the Executive Principal of Vanke Meisha\nAcademy has been emphasizing the significance of students’ cultivation of\nChinese identity. According to her, international education itself means cross\ncultural understanding and cooperation. It encourages each person to share with\nothers their own cultural specialties. At this moment, if your hands are empty,\nwould you know who you are? What special contribution can you make. What are\nyour strengths? Why do we exist? … That is why our Academy offers many students\naccess to so many associations and interests groups to support the learning of\nboth Chinese culture and other cultures. \n\n","\n\n\t\n \n \n\n\t  \n \n\n\t\n \n \n\n\t  \n \n\n\t\n \n \n\n\t  \n "]', N'[""]', N'[""]')
GO
GO
INSERT INTO [dbo].[articals] ([id], [title], [contenttype], [author], [publishtime], [content], [content-img], [content-img-trans]) VALUES (N'20160719142402', N'2016 High School Entrance Admission  (万科梅沙书院2016中招喜报)', N'1', N'Admin', N'2016-09-30 10:09:55.0000000', N'["\n\tOn July 18, 2016 Shenzhen high school admission results was announced by Shenzhen municipal office of high school admission. According to it, the admission line of Vanke Meisha Academy was: 362, which was the highest score among all the international schools in Shenzhen. 100 students were admitted by Vanke Meisha Academy: 29 of them scored more than 430, 43 of them scored more than 419, 58 of them scored more than 400, and the average score was 407, which was 63 points higher than the average score of all the students in Shenzhen (344). As a school established for merely one year, Vanke Meisha Academy would like to express its gratitude for the trust placed by parents and students. ","\n\t7月18日，从深圳市招生考试办公室传来捷报！在公布的《2016年我市高中阶段学校第二批录取标准》中，万科梅沙书院中招录取分数线高达362分，在其他同类国际学校（班）中独占鳌头！100名录取学生中，高分段学生成绩耀目，430分以上共29名，419分以上共43名，400分以上共58名，均分达407分，超出全市总均分63分（全市中考均分为344分）。万科梅沙书院作为一所成立仅一年的国际学校，首次参加中考招生，获得如此优异的成绩实属难得！ ","\n\tMeantime, the academy provides 150 offers to selected students through other means. Since this April, we have already conducted three independent admission examinations and offers have been sent to 100 excellent students out of 1,000 student candidates. The admission examinations consist of written test, English interview, and psychological test, aiming to find the most competitive students with global competence. At the moment, we are providing limited offers to the students who had gained 419 in total and Grade B in English test in 2016 Shenzhen high school entrance examination. Until July 18th, 76 eligible students have applied for that. ","\n\t在中考招生硕果累累的同时，梅沙书院向社会开放150个自主招生名额，目前的招生成果令人振奋！梅沙书院从4月份以来已成功举办三次自主招生考试，共有近千名初三毕业生报名，通过笔试、英语面试、思维测试等高标准、多维度的测评中择优录取了100余名优秀考生。日前针对中考总分419分以上且数学和英语成绩B等级以上的中考生特别开通绿色报名通道，截止到7月18日已有76名学生报名。 ","\n\tVanke Meisha Academy would like to express its gratitude for the trust placed by parents and students. During the past 2015-2016 academic year, students from Vanke Meisha Academy have achieved a lot both in academics and personal growth in 2016 United States Academic Decathlon, 2016 International Mathematical Modeling Challenge, 2016 National Linguistics Olympiad, Imagine Cup Earth coding competition,National High School Academic Speech and Debate Tournament, and so on. The academy has already passed a series of strict examinations set by Cambridge International Center and became a Cambridge school, which enables its authorities to offer IGCSE and A-Level courses. VMA has also beenauthorized to be awarding center of “The Duke of Edinburgh International Award” ","\n\t万科梅沙书院在2016招生中获得的辉煌成绩，有力证明了社会各界对万科梅沙书院一年来办学成效的积极认可！在过去的2015-2016学年，万科梅沙书院在USAD美国学术十项全能竞赛、国际数学建模挑战赛、国际语言学奥林匹克竞赛、微软创新杯大赛、全国中学生学术演讲辩论赛等多项国内外学术竞赛中均取得令人瞩目的成绩。万科梅沙书院通过各项考核，成为剑桥国际考试中心，将有资质提供IGCSE高中基础学历课程和A-Level高中高级学历课程。万科梅沙书院也已成为爱丁堡公爵奖励计划的独立授奖机构，为学生提供高水准的国际学术和活动平台。 ","\n\tIn the coming 2016-2017 academic year, with the mission of “cultivating global citizens and leaders with Chinese identity”, Vanke Meisha Academy will continue to advance its curriculum by strengthening its passion and courage for international education and establishing 15 AP courses. The academy conducts teaching based on students’needs, personal characters, and individual progress to ensure their all-rounded and promising development! ","\n\t2016-2017学年，万科梅沙书院将继续充满对国际教育的热情和勇气，秉持“培养具有中国精神的国际公民和领袖人才”的培养目标，开设15门美国大学先修AP课程，进一步优化梅沙书院独特的国际化课程体系。书院还将根据学生的学业水平、兴趣专长进行按需施教、分层教学，促进学生的全面发展、个性发展和卓越发展！ ","\n\tWith the stable and marvelous teaching and administrative team, Vanke Meisha Academy has been recruiting excellent teachers globally, including our Foreign Principal Dr. Peter Warsaw and other 26 foreign teachers. There will be nearly 100 teachers and the teacher-student ratio will be 1:4. ","\n\t万科梅沙书院在保持上学年稳定、优秀的师资队伍的同时，不断吸收具有丰富国际教育经验的中外教师，其中包括外方校长、哈佛博士Peter Warsaw在内的26名外教已全部到位，教职工总人数近100人，师生比1：4。 ","\n\tVanke Meisha Academy highly appreciate these parents and students, who has the same and profound understanding on international education. We believe we will create a wonderful future together! ","\n\t万科梅沙书院欢迎并感谢对国际教育有着深刻理解，与我们有着共同理想的优秀学生和家长加入，一起创造日新月异的未来！ ","\n\tVanke Meisha Academy ","\n\tJuly 19, 2016 ","\n\t2016年7月19日 ","\n\tAppendix: ","\n\t万科梅沙书院  \n\t附件：  "]', N'[""]', N'[""]')
GO
GO
INSERT INTO [dbo].[articals] ([id], [title], [contenttype], [author], [publishtime], [content], [content-img], [content-img-trans]) VALUES (N'201704240843221', N'【VMA风筝节】忙趁东风放纸鸢', N'26', N'yumingmei', N'2017-04-24 08:42:00.0000000', N'["人间四月，已是春风和煦，天朗气清。深圳向来冬天极短，从冬天到春天，仿佛只需要一场大梦的时间。一场春雨过后，昨夜还是光秃秃的树枝，今日树梢就挂满了新芽儿。春天里，最不缺的就是嫩芽儿般的希望，我们愿相伴于缕缕春风，寄愿在风筝之上，让希望飘向远方。梅沙书院中国传统文化中心借着春日里和煦的微风，举办了春季的传统活动——放风筝。","这是古人描写孩童在春日里放飞纸鸢的景象。试想那时春草盈盈，堤岸旁杨柳绿如烟，轻轻地拂着地面，仿佛在春天的烟雾里醉得直摇晃，三两孩童下学归来忙于放纸鸢之景。春日里的纸鸢在青天之上，身随雾气缭绕，风拂过纸鸢上的铜哨发出泠泠之声，如同拨筝弄弦一般。","风筝又称“纸鸢”，传统的风筝是用竹子和宣纸制成。制作纸鸢是中国的传统技艺，制作过程概括起来只有四个字：扎、糊、绘、放，但却蕴含着中华民族千千万万工匠的心血，代代延续至今。","想要纯手工制作一个风筝绝非易事，本次活动重点体验绘风筝和放风筝的乐趣。大家选择自己喜欢的图案和颜色，三三两两一组，低头专注于笔尖的描抹，完成属于自己的风筝。绚丽的色彩在笔尖流转，风筝的底板渐渐缤纷起来。鲜明透亮的赤与黄是最受欢迎的，千百年来这两种颜色被广泛地运用在风筝和其他民间艺术上，人们在这两种色彩上寄寓了吉祥如意的美好祝福。古往今来，中国人的对美好生活的向往依然是如此的单纯如一。","由于春风柔和，放飞风筝成了最大的困难。大家不断尝试各种方式将风筝放飞，甚至搬来了单车帮忙。一次次奔跑，一次次调整，一次次重头再来，终于，有些同学的风筝徐徐升上天空，在和风中轻轻舞动着。夕阳的余晖带着暖意丝丝缕缕的照在每一张年轻的脸上，照进每一双充满希望的眼中。","伴随着风筝一次次的飞起又落下，夕阳已经将最后的温暖映在天边。半边红的天际飘着几只风筝，随着春风的抚动翩翩起舞。空气中依然氤氲着清新的泥土气息，那些随风漫舞的风筝将承载着春天的希望，飘向远方。","草长莺飞二月天， 拂堤杨柳醉春烟。 儿童散学归来早， 忙趁东风放纸鸢。 "]', N'["http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170424/6362861968354424111198486.png","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170424/6362861996882523654168590.jpg","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170424/6362861996887203954452671.jpg","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170424/6362861996879403456710100.jpg","http://img.vma.edu.cn/image/20170424/6362861973784263578256842.png"]', N'["","","","",""]')
