INSERT INTO [dbo].[articals] ([id], [title], [contenttype], [author], [publishtime], [content], [content-img], [content-img-trans]) VALUES (N'20160128115105', N'For VMA, For Better Future', N'4', N'Admin', N'2016-02-01 16:19:57.0000000', N'["\n\t---\nSplendid Show of the First Student Union Team of Vanke Meisha Academy\n","\n\n\tThe first VankeMeisha Academy\n(hereinafter referred to as “the Academy”) student union team contest has lasted\nfor almost 2 months by November 23. All competitors, from the campaign speech, medium-term\npracticing activities and current achievementdisplay and report, had kept\nmodifying the schemes and improving themselves for not only election but also\nfeeling no regret. Under the tense atmosphere with changing votes on screen,\nthe Team A led by Tang Ziying and Liu Zijin won other\ncompetitors with the gap of 0.04 and thus becoming the Academy’s first student\nunion team.\n","\n\n\tStudent Zhang Yaxuan and Tan Fengyu\nwere finally selected as the Chinese/English bilingual host and the conference was\ncomposed of six parts: 1. Summary report of practicing activities by all teams;\n2. All teams should assign the representatives to have QA link; 3. The\nstudent union should organize a committee to propose one problem to each team;\n4. All teams should conduct QA link with attended students. 5. All teams\nshould conduct the final speech or activities for votes. 6. All students and\nteachers of the Academy should vote and the process and result will be displayed\non the screen.\n","\n\n\tFirstly, all teams should conduct report and final demonstration\nabout the 3-week practicing. Tang Ziying, Chairman,\nand Liu Zijin, Vice Chairman, had summarized the Team A’s practicing named “Campus\nculture construction”. Under the leadership of Team A, our academy had launched\nclub demonstration day, SUPER QUIZ and dormitory decoration activities to fully\nexert the effects of all students and also promote the Academy’s unique campus\nculture. Secondly, Li Xinyao, Chairman, and Lin Zhenghao, Vice Chairman of Team\nWEE, had reported the management process of checker depot and derivatives of campus\nto summarize its success experience and shortcomings. Finally, Team DOTS had\nintroduced their practicing theme - execution of campus principle using\nexquisite video, covering the clothing, electric equipment, dormitory and\ncampus hygiene and principle of self-study at night. As campus principle\nmanagement is always a key but tough problem, DOTS tried its best to protect\nthe students’individuality and freedom and also fully fulfill the supervision responsibility\nto ensure that all rules and regulations of academy be followed.\n","\n\n\tIn the QA link after report, two\nrepresentatives were separately selected by each Team to conduct QA with\nother members and answer the questions from attended teachers and students. All\nteams are proposing sharp questions and the witty answers also won the\napplauses from all. In the canvassing link, all teams tried to express their\nspirit and unique value through wonderful dances and speeches to show their\ncharms to all.\n","\n\n\tThe demonstration stage was followed by the voting by all students\nand teachers and there was real-time display of votes of all teams on screen.\nThis voting not only showed the confirmation and support to\nefforts of all teams, but also showed the choices of the Academy and its\nfurther students with respect to self management. All students and teachers, as\nthe Academy’s members, were\njointly building the culture and spirit value of school, would select the\ncommittee to have the best expression of spirituality and value of campus,\nstudents and teachers. In the few minutes, the votes of Team A and DOTS were\nquite close and finally, Team A won this election by weak advantage of 41.43% and 41.39%.\n","\n\n\tFinally, Mr. Li Zhiguo, Assistant of the principal, had summarized the\nelection of student union. He firstly celebrated for the election winning of\nTeam A and then answered the questions of students about this election. He also\napplauded for the good self-control, execution and leadership of all teams in\nthe competition, all of which may be converted to the self competitiveness and\nhelp the students realize their dreams after three years.\n","\n\n\tThe Academy’s first student union selection ended and the\nstudents have shown their good qualities such as good thinking, devotion and\ncourage to undertake. The first student union\nselection was held in form of teams to help cultivate the team spirit of\nstudents, actively promote the cooperation and communication between students\nand make them drive the team with their ability, unite and keep improving, so\nas to develop their abilities in cooperation and leadership. The competition\nended and we hoped the student union may have active guidance to the students\nand teachers with respect to work, activity and contest, provide practical\nlearning and living services, promote the spirit and connotation of striving\nand progressing and cultivate the different thinking modes, so as to create a\nbright future with the powerful execution force.\n","\n\n\tPrepared by: Yan Ziru, Zhu Liyan (VMA\nCampus Media Center · Journal Dept.)\n","\n\n\tPhoto source: VMA\nPhotography Studio\n","\n\n\tTutor: Wu\nNingxin\n","\n\n\t \n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t\n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t\n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t\n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t\n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t \n \n\n\t\n "]', N'[""]', N'[""]')
